  "2337990": {
    "name": "Kohlrabi Starship",
    "steam_appid": 2337990,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337990/extras/c0bde1ac0d4e321acebe7ce6c8a82888.avif?t=1770922482\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337990/extras_big/c0bde1ac0d4e321acebe7ce6c8a82888.avif?t=1770922482 width=800 height=215 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kohlrabi Starship 是一款悠闲的星际旅行耕种游戏。在这里，你在努力复苏母星生态系统的同时，还不忘了寻找真爱和探索未知的星系！你将作为温室太空船的船长，开始冒险旅程，探索神秘的星球，寻找稀有植物和濒临灭绝的动物。将它们带回你的家园，慢慢地把曾经的沙漠转化成一个再次蓬勃发展的生态系统。但这绝非易事！你需要修复太空船、收集资源和能源核心、出售庄稼赚钱、与村民和好奇的太空旅行者结交朋友，并相互支持。适应每个星球的气候和昼夜循环。按照你的喜好装饰和布置你的太空船。也许你甚至会在旅途中找到爱情。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所以快戴上你的园艺手套，准备好踏上一场在宇宙中恢复自然的旅程！不知你将如何塑造这些星球？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337990/extras/e09c663fdbc866efd92b1ac7b0415134.poster.avif?t=1770922482\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337990/extras/e09c663fdbc866efd92b1ac7b0415134.webm?t=1770922482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索星系 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >修复你祖母的太空船，让它恢复昔日的荣耀，并在星际间旅行！游戏中的每一次通关都将让你探索不同的星球。发现新的植物、动物和外星生命，并将它们带上飞船，创建你的濒危动植物方舟。你会在星系的最深处发现什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337990/extras/f1e104e10f4d0e3167c1c7173741aa5d.poster.avif?t=1770922482\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337990/extras/f1e104e10f4d0e3167c1c7173741aa5d.webm?t=1770922482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>复苏生态系统 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择引入哪些植物，并让它们与周围的环境相互影响，要么迅速扩散，要么消失。拯救濒危的动物和外星生命，并通过战略性繁育，来深刻影响本土的生态系统。改造沙漠，带回曾经失去的绿色天堂！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>定制你的太空船 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择在飞船上培育哪些物种，并利用被遗忘的技术调整太空船的温度和光照条件。加快时间，或烹饪能让你连续几天都保持清醒的神奇料理。收集和建造家具、地板和墙壁，让你感觉像家一样舒适。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337990/extras/0322a94e1f2d9fd70fd2bd91b1f6b9a7.poster.avif?t=1770922482\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337990/extras/0322a94e1f2d9fd70fd2bd91b1f6b9a7.webm?t=1770922482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>寻找爱情 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与各种各样的角色互动，帮助他们解决问题，建立关系，并寻找爱情。在太空深处，你并非独自一人 - 去寻找你的社区吧！这包括对你的坠毁太空船开出罚单的闷闷不乐的警察，以及为自我意识相关的哲学问题而挣扎的可爱的机器人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337990/extras/cc1803854cedd8ac04a2bb7716a24988.avif?t=1770922482\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337990/extras_big/cc1803854cedd8ac04a2bb7716a24988.avif?t=1770922482 width=800 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>养殖动物 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驯服、命名和繁殖宠物和动物！你有没有幻想过你的宠物能一直跟在你的身边？或者你是否曾经认为你最喜欢的颜色正好适合小猫的毛发颜色，即使它是绿色、粉色或蓝色？繁殖任意毛色的宠物，让它跟随你的冒险，并给予它们应得的所有爱。但请确保当你不注意时它们不要吃掉你最珍贵的庄稼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337990/extras/251f82f2fc1f4c8df5e9e2377f113c48.poster.avif?t=1770922482\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337990/extras/251f82f2fc1f4c8df5e9e2377f113c48.webm?t=1770922482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>还有更多 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个人都可以在Kohlrabi Starship上找到属于自己的乐趣。你将决定如何度过你的时间。挖掘和收集资源，修复你的太空船并开发新的农业技术。为你的朋友烹饪新菜肴。完成你的外星生命百科全书。摆脱银河帝国的影响。一切由你决定！</p>",
